nodes.text: P. Dantari was a member of the Liana Liberators. His P. Dantari name was an alias used as part of the Liberator's attempt to pose as members of the Alderaanian Biological Research Institute when they came to the Cularin system during the Clone Wars. He contacted the Starchaser IV when the Liberators were attacked by mynocks It is unknown what his real identity was.
